.TH LOOTSHEET-TUI 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-tui \\- Open the full-screen terminal dashboard shell
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet tui [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet tui

Opens the first full-screen LootSheet dashboard shell using tcell.
This slice is read-only and currently focuses on screen lifecycle, resize-safe boxed panels, theme groundwork, and footer help.

Keys:
  q       quit the dashboard
  Esc     quit the dashboard
  Ctrl+L  force a full redraw
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for tui
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet(1)
